Key Considerations and Limits Action Allowed? Key Limits / Considerations Future →right arrow → Queueable Yes Limited to 1 System.enqueueJob in async context. Queueable →right arrow → Future Yes 50 future calls allowed per transaction. Future →right arrow → Future No Will throw: "Future method cannot be called from a future or batch method". Queueable →right arrow → Queueable Yes Only 1 child job can exist for each parent queueable job.